title: Hundreds protest in Sacramento over video of police shooting
text:
Hundreds protest in Sacramento over video of police shooting Friday, March 23, 2018 - 01:09 
Newly released video footage of police killing an unarmed black man in a barrage of gunfine in California sparks street protests that gridlock traffic for hours. No reporter narration. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
